name: LocateInternationalSpaceStation
0:
”Alexa, ask international space station locator to find the international space station”
”Alexa, ask international space station locator to tell me where the international space station is”
”Alexa, open international space station locator”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: international space station locator
des:
This skill gives the current location of the international space station (ISS) in real time. It may be above your city!

Fun fact, the ISS travels at 17130 mph and orbits around the Earth every 93 minutes!

I am a 9-year old. I like developing alexa skills. I hope you enjoy this skill.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
